# NOTE — intentionally NOT gitignored:
#   .claude/  .cursor/  .codex/  .gemini/  .agents/  .kiro/  .opencode/  .windsurf/
#
# These are generated by `pnpm build` from source/skills/, but committed
# to git on purpose so that `npx skills add` can install the plugin via
# git-clone without requiring Node/pnpm on the consumer's machine.
# CI enforces that source and outputs stay in sync — see .github/workflows/ci.yml.
